      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Roughly chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong></p>",
